sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as API Client
    participant API as FastAPI Application
    participant Service as Service Layer
    participant DB as Database
    participant Billing as External Billing System

    Client->>API: POST /transactions
    API->>Service: Validate & transform request
    Service->>DB: Insert Transaction
    DB-->>Service: Transaction saved
    Service->>Billing: Send billing event (amount, property, concept)
    Billing-->>Service: Billing confirmation
    Service-->>API: Return created transaction + billing status
    API-->>Client: 201 Created (JSON)